{
  "stem": "21089.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And nobody knew where they went, so I went with the army units.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he said, go east.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "East, everything is going east to protect eastern border because from east, Russia started the war.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So those certain units were assigned.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But where east?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "What east?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Nobody knew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went to and I end up on 17 on-- in Lutsk.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is in east Poland.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at that time, the Russian march into the Poland.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this was the end of the war for me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What happened to you?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon me?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that time, I went to town.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I, I didn't know anybody.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't have any money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't have anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, and, you see, I-- when I left home, I-- because tran-- tran-- transportation was very bad.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the fire department, one unit was evacuated, supposed to be evacuated to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was a volunteer fire de-- firemen, and I was-- I had to report to the army unit.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they allowed me to go with them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I had a bike, bicycle, and a backpack on, on me, and a bike.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this was my transportation because without bike, I would have to walk and not to be able to do-- not to be able to go anyplace.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So as I said, on 17 I end up in the-- and little by little, I realize-- actually, the first money which I got, I realized then my father had some clients in, in Lutsk because this was every sack of flour had to have a label, a big label.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in Lutsk were very many flour mills.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I know that we printed, so I realize that some money must have been coming because I'd been constantly printing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I went to two that were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
